Appendix B: Synthesis Protocol (Condensed)



1. Au$_{13}$ glutathione clusters: HAuCl$_4$ + glutathione, NaBH$_4$ reduction, SEC purification.
2. Ligand exchange: Au$_{13}$-glutathione + 100‑fold excess DmT in anhydrous DMSO, 12 h, 25 °C.
3. Ac doping: Add carrier‑free $^{227}$AcCl$_3$ (0.008 at% relative to Au), stir 6 h.
4. Aerogel: TMOS sol‑gel with 0.5 wt% Au$_{13}$ DmT‑Ac, supercritical CO$_2$ drying.
5. Cavity mounting: Polish to $\lambda/10$, coat with Ta$_2$O$_5$/SiO$_2$, cool to 1.5 K.

---

